Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:22:59.91,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}To unchain the mystic rites
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:02.16,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}I'm calling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:07.77,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}I'm on my way to find the eternal verities
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:12.95,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Exploding all the teardrops by the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.61,0:23:18.80,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}I can feel my heart beating
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.85,0:23:28.79,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}I can see my fate all spinning around beyond the time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:32.24,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Rise up to the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:34.88,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Like a butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:37.50,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Show me what's inside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:40.15,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Don't ever let go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.60,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Shining stars will guide me to somewhere high
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:50.97,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Finding the truth beyond the heaven's door
